marketing: Shell Mysella S6 SM has been specially developed to give extended oil life even in applications with very sour gases, such as those with high H2S content. Shell Mysella S6 SM uses a formulation which has been optimised to resist the corrosive and oxidative effects of sulphuric and halogenic acids which are often present in these environments.
